[div class=p 
	"This movie uses a variety of 
	(__wikiLink|displaytext=sequence breaks and shortcuts|href=/GameResources/N64/ZeldaOcarinaOfTime)
	" to complete the game in under an hour using a minimal number of inventory and quest items. Of central interest are the ability to glitch through the Door of Time, meaning that no dungeons need to be entered as young Link, and a memory manipulation glitch known as the Reverse Bottle Adventure, allowing the medallions collected from adult Link's dungeons to be pulled out of thin air; therefore the only dungeon that is ever entered in this run is Ganon's Castle.
	$LF
]div
